00:35:35,760 --> 00:35:39,760
Which I think is counterproductive to everyone's instinct listening to it.

613
00:35:39,760 --> 00:35:39,840
Yes.

614
00:35:41,460 --> 00:35:46,900
Less proactive, more ability to be massively fast at reacting.

615
00:35:47,540 --> 00:35:51,020
Our job is to minimize harm overall.

616
00:35:51,810 --> 00:35:56,610
But the more proactive we are, the more we start adding bile next back in the system.

