00:37:13,010 --> 00:37:17,010
But here, the thing that's – this is fantastic.

646
00:37:17,010 --> 00:37:26,140
The thing that is important about this principle is that the modern tester is disallowed

647
00:37:28,030 --> 00:37:31,630
to create significant bottlenecks back in the system.

