shipping and then that's having to be rolled back, it's not just QA.

661
00:38:44,350 --> 00:38:45,310
It's going to be concerned.

662
00:38:45,310 --> 00:38:46,350
It's going to be the business.

663
00:38:47,230 --> 00:38:49,710
We're not going to – now, but the thing at that point in time,

664
00:38:49,710 --> 00:38:57,710
and I love when we get to that bottleneck or that decision point, rather, because what you have to

