00:42:27,280 --> 00:42:32,320
What are some other things that you've done to support this principle,

713
00:42:33,060 --> 00:42:35,060
or that you've seen done to accelerate the team?

714
00:42:36,180 --> 00:42:43,380
The single most important thing is get folks moving up front.

715
00:42:43,380 --> 00:42:48,900
The second most important thing – so these are very tactical things that I've discovered

716
00:42:48,900 --> 00:42:49,700
work very well.

