00:42:50,700 --> 00:42:58,900
Shift to a flow model, not a Scrum or a waterfall model.

718
00:42:59,890 --> 00:43:01,330
Do one check-in-a-time.

719
00:43:02,660 --> 00:43:06,100
Create a process where one check-in-a-time goes to stage,

720
00:43:06,820 --> 00:43:11,460
and then that gets validated and goes to production.

721
00:43:12,300 --> 00:43:20,140
Create a mechanism where you're using test and production to drive automatically your rollback

