00:43:23,170 --> 00:43:34,060
One of the biggest issues that I've seen is a lot of teams, they're still heavy on the proactivity

724
00:43:34,060 --> 00:43:39,420
and have it invested in the ability to solidly roll back automatically.

725
00:43:41,150 --> 00:43:42,190
It's a forward only.

726
00:43:42,910 --> 00:43:47,780
And once you detect harm, you've got to roll it back.

727
00:43:49,250 --> 00:43:56,610
But what you'll find is that a lot of the situations – things that we've done in the past,

728
00:43:56,610 --> 00:44:01,730
the traditional testing methods – were a waste of time.

729
00:44:02,780 --> 00:44:03,020
Yes.

