00:44:20,240 --> 00:44:24,480
It's even part of Scrum that teams don't take advantage of properly, is the retrospective.

735
00:44:25,490 --> 00:44:26,130
Yes.

736
00:44:26,130 --> 00:44:33,810
It's a method for the team to discuss and discover and sometimes solve the bottlenecks

737
00:44:33,810 --> 00:44:34,370
in the system.

738
00:44:34,930 --> 00:44:39,010
The other thing that, again, that – I mean, you asked what have I done.

739
00:44:39,730 --> 00:44:48,100
One of the things that I've done is deeply invested in the telemetry and the data.

740
00:44:48,100 --> 00:44:48,820
Yes.

