00:44:48,820 --> 00:44:59,540
Because one of the ways to really accelerate the team is to kill the theoretical discussions.

742
00:45:04,290 --> 00:45:07,410
More than hours, I would say – I'm old.

743
00:45:07,650 --> 00:45:15,820
At this point in time, it probably is, months of my time in my career has just been lost

